Odaily Planet Daily News AI VC Agent HeyAni officially debuted at the Protfolio Day held by Animoca Brands in Hong Kong. HeyAni is developed by Animoca Brands and FLock.io. It aims to use decentralized AI technology to provide projects with more comprehensive and professional investment and operation advice, and lower the entry threshold for Web3 entrepreneurs and investors.
HeyAni's technical foundation is fully built by FLock.io, relying on its decentralized AI training and verification network to achieve three core functions:
Web3 project parties can submit business plans, and AI will conduct intelligent evaluation and provide optimization suggestions;
Investors can query token codes, and AI will generate relevant analysis and comments based on token public information;
HeyAni Alpha is regularly analyzed by AI and publishes a list of high-potential projects.
As the technical foundation of HeyAni, FLock.io provides a complete set of decentralized AI training and computing solutions to ensure the transparency, fairness and verifiability of AI evaluation. HeyAni is based on the AI ​​model trained by FLock.io platform Mainnet Task 2 and Testnet Task 16, integrating Animoca Brands' investment and operation experience in more than 540 Web3 ecosystem projects to create the first enterprise-level + retail-end encrypted investment analysis platform based on decentralized AI, pushing the Web3 ecosystem towards a smarter and fairer new stage. The Beta version is now online.
